 Gear2D Readme

 - Installation

 Gear2D might be installed using INSTALL document provided or http://gear2d.sourceforge.net/


 - Running Gear2D

 Gear2D is meant to be runned inside a game root directory, that is, where lives a file 
 called gear2d.yaml.

   . Windows

   You'll need to make a shortcut for the gear2d executable inside your game folder
   and double click on it.

   . Linux-like
   
   Navigate through the game folder using a terminal and type gear2d
